      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "# Welcome, Human! 👋\n\n**Twilite is your visual thinking space.**\n\nForget about JSON and schemas for a moment. This is a place where you can:\n\n- **Map your thoughts** visually on an infinite canvas\n- **Connect ideas** with meaningful relationships\n- **Build systems** that grow with your understanding\n- **Think spatially** instead of linearly\n\nThink of it like:\n- A whiteboard that remembers\n- A mind map that can execute\n- A notebook where pages can talk to each other\n\n**Start exploring →**",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "b2c3d4e5-f6a7-4b8c-9d0e-1f2a3b4c5d6e",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "What Can You Build?",
      "position": {
        "x": -619.2664700541632,
        "y": 62.8795104600874
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 420,
      "color": "#2e7d32",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "top",
