        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [
        {
          "key": "out",
          "label": "Out",
          "type": "content"
        }
      ],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## What Can You Build?\n\n### 📚 Personal Knowledge Base\nCapture notes, link concepts, build your second brain\n\n### 🎯 Project Planning\nBreak down goals, track dependencies, visualize progress\n\n### 🧠 Brainstorming\nFree-form idea generation with emergent structure\n\n### 📖 Story Development\nCharacters, plots, world-building with relationships\n\n### 🗺️ Learning Maps\nSubjects connect, prerequisites emerge naturally\n\n### 🔄 Workflows\nProcess steps with decision points and feedback loops\n\n### 💡 Idea Gardens\nCapture seeds, watch them grow into systems",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "c3d4e5f6-a7b8-4c9d-0e1f-2a3b4c5d6e7f",
      "type": "markdown",
      "label": "Your First Graph",
      "position": {
        "x": -1100.946491567872,
        "y": 114.99958529994456
      },
      "width": 360,
      "height": 380,
      "color": "#2e7d32",
      "ports": [
        {
          "id": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "direction": "input",
          "dataType": "flow",
          "position": {
            "side": "top",
            "offset": 0.5
          }
        }
      ],
      "inputs": [
        {
          "key": "in",
          "label": "In",
          "type": "flow"
        }
      ],
      "outputs": [],
      "visible": true,
      "showLabel": true,
      "data": {
        "markdown": "## Create Your First Graph\n\n### The Easy Way\nJust tell me what you want to build:\n\n*\"Create a graph for planning my book project\"*\n\n*\"I want to map out my learning path for web development\"*\n\n*\"Help me organize my research on climate change\"*\n\nI'll build it for you, then you can evolve it.\n\n### What Happens Next\n1. I'll create nodes for your main concepts\n2. Connect them with relationships\n3. Add structure (categories, flows, hierarchies)\n4. You can ask me to modify, expand, or reorganize\n\n**The graph grows with your thinking.**",
        "memo": "",
        "link": "",
        "html": "",
        "svg": "",
        "isRoot": false,
        "root": false
      }
    },
    {
